{{Quote|You ever do the Belsavis Run, Han?|[[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] to [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]|<ref name="Children of the Jedi">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref>}}
The '''Belsavis Run''' was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]] that linked the planet [[Tekurr'k]] in the [[Senex sector/Legends|Senex sector]] to [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]] in the [[Bozhnee sector/Legends|Bozhnee sector]]. Mara Jade implied to have done it on her first trip to Belsavis, around the time of the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]].<ref name="Children of the Jedi" />

